                  <ab type="history">Gadām. At least 25 monks live in the community; there is a  well-established church school. 
                     A more recent church dedicated to <persName type="tabot" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS9162TaklaHa">Takla Haymanot</persName>, associated with the monastery, is located in the vicinity.
</ab>
                  
